{"ts":"2026-05-29T22:28:41.297Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-wr74"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"Calendar positional-date and impossible-deadline UX: pm calendar 2026-06-15 hard-errors; --deadline 2026-02-30 silently rolls to Mar 2"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Two agent-hostile calendar UX issues from dogfood: (1) pm calendar <ISO-date> errors 'view must be agenda|day|week|month' with no did-you-mean — should route an ISO-looking positional to --date or hint it. (2) pm create --deadline 2026-02-30 silently overflows to 2026-03-02 (JS Date rollover) with no warning, while 2026-13-99 is correctly rejected — validate calendar-day validity and reject/warn on rollover."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","calendar","never-block"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-05-29T22:28:41.297Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-05-29T22:28:41.297Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"1e2c2a39294e6b23b898dd3f1dba6306365caa1e4cd4c45075ef0b5a0c1664bf","message":""}
